nodes.text: Iden Versio's TIE/ln space superiority starfighter

During the Galactic Civil War, Commander Iden Versio of Inferno Squad utilized a specialized TIE/ln space superiority starfighter with upgraded weapons and Inferno Squad markings. Versio used the TIE fighter during the attack on Fondor.

Iden Versio's TIE fighter first appeared in the third campaign mission titled The Dauntless when the full game released on for special access owners on November 9, 2017. In an update on January 16, 2018, her TIE fighter debuted in multiplayer and can be selected to play as by players.
